---
categories:
  - Spring
tags:
  - MapperScannerConfigurer
date:
  - 2022-11-28 8:54:41
---

<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MapperFactoryBean</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的一个问题是每个接口映射都需要手动添加，需要用到的映射器较多的话，采用这种配置方式就会很低效。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">为了解决这个问题，我们可以使用</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MapperScannerConfigurer</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，让它扫描特定的包，自动帮我们成批的创建映射器。这样一来，就能大大减少配置的工作量，我们就不要手动添加接口映射了（减少了</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                    style="color:maroon">mapperInterface</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的参数添加，</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">即同时封装了</span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">sql</span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">S</span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">ession</span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Factory</span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">和</span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Mapper</span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的映射代理</span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MapperScannerConfigurer</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">对象（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">org.mybatis.spring.</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">mapper.MapperScanner</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Configurer</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">），通过循环找到</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">basePackage</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">包中所有接口，调用</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">sqlSession.getMapper</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">创建接口对象，并把对象的代理放在容器中</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><img
        src="data:image/png;base64,"
        style="height:582px; width:837px"><br></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:#70ad47"><strong>示例</strong></span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#a5a5a5">&lt;!--</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:72px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#a5a5a5"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;bean</span>&nbsp;<span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">id="userMapper"</span>&nbsp;<span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">class="org.mybatis.spring.mapper.MapperFactoryBean"&gt;</span></span></span>
</p>
<p style="margin-left:108px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#a5a5a5">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;!--</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">指定配置的</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">sqlSessionFactory--&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:72px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="color:#a5a5a5">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;property</span>&nbsp;<span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">name="</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">sqlsessionFactoryBeanName</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">"</span>&nbsp;<span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">value="sqlSessionFactory"/&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:108px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#a5a5a5">&nbsp;&nbsp; <span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;!--</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">加入接口</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">--&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:108px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#a5a5a5">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;property</span>&nbsp;<span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">name="mapperInterface"</span>&nbsp;<span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">value="</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">com.exi.</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">dao.User</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Mapper</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">"/&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:72px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="color:#a5a5a5">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;property</span>&nbsp;<span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">name="mapperInterface"</span>&nbsp;<span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">value="</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">com.exi.</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">dao.</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">StudentMapper</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">"/&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:108px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#a5a5a5">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; …</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:72px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#a5a5a5">&lt;/bean&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#a5a5a5">--&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:#70ad47">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#538135"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;!--</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">配置</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MapperScannerConfigurer</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">对象</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">--&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:blue">&lt;bean</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:blue">class</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:black">=</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#78230c">"org.mybatis.spring.</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#78230c">mapper.MapperScanner</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:#78230c">Configurer"</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:blue">&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:#538135">&lt;!--</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:#538135">指定配置的</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#538135">sqlSessionFactory--&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span
        style="font-size:12.0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:blue">&lt;property</span></span>&nbsp;<span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:blue">name</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:black">=</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:maroon">"</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:maroon">sqlsessionFactoryBeanName</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:maroon">"</span></span>&nbsp;<span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:blue">value</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:black">=</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:maroon">"sqlSessionFactory"</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:blue">/&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:72px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#538135"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;!--</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">指定</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Mapper</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">对象接口所在的包名</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">--&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:72px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:blue">&lt;property</span></span>&nbsp;<span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:blue">name</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:black">=</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:maroon">"</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:maroon">basePackage</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:maroon">"</span></span>&nbsp;<span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:blue">value</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:black">=</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:maroon">"</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:maroon">com.exi.dao</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:maroon">"</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:blue">/&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
